<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> kō-vicaiya-ka
<lb n="2" break="no"/>mpa-vikkiramaparumaṟku yā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇṭu patiṉēḻ-āvatu
<lb n="4"/>Innāṭṭ-uṭaiya <hi rend="grantha">pṛthi</hi><orig>ya</orig>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṅkaraiyarum Ivar tē
<lb n="6" break="no"/>viyār Ilāṭapperuntē
<lb n="7" break="no"/>viyārum taṅkaḷ maka<choice><unclear>ṉ</unclear><unclear>ḷ</unclear></choice>
<lb n="8"/>Ayyak=kuṭṭi Aṭikaḷukku
	</p>
